    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Dwarf&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Greed&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Some illusionists are experts in manipulating light and darkness. Characters with this trait cast spells with the darkness, light, or shadow<sup>UM</sup> descriptor at +1 caster level.<br /><br /> Dwarves can take this trait in place of greed. Elves can take this trait in place of elven magic, also gaining the fetchling's spell-like abilities<sup>ARG</sup> racial trait. Gnomes can take this trait in place of gnome magic. Halflings can take this trait in place of weapon familiarity. Half-orcs can take this trait in place of intimidating, also gaining the gnome's illusion resistance racial trait.</p>",
